metadata.description: Edbangerz is a collection of 666 grim-dark fantasy, heavy metal inspired NFTs. Spat forth from the immaterium, the ironclad hordes of Edbangerz will march ever forward to the beat of total armageddon. Do you have the strength of will to stop them?  The first generative set brought to you by metal artist Spearhead. With a decade worth of experience designing for some of the biggest names in metal, hardcore and punk you can rest assured that each of the Edz will be hard as nails. Blending the iconic heavy metal aesthetic with a love of both high fantasy and the ancient and medieval history of cultures around the world, this love-letter collection to all things gnarly is sure to feel right at home on the Ethereum. The march of the Edbangerz is just beginning, as is the world in which they inhabit. Love and glory to everyone who joins us on this adventure into the darkness.
metadata.name: Edbangerz - Ed Strife
